{{Toy-stub}}

'''Imaginarium SA''' is a [[Spain|Spanish]] company that operates a chain of [[toy store]]s. It sells various toys comprising wheel, furniture, and child care toys to various customers, including educational institutions, such as schools, nurseries, or playgroups. The company operates 348 outlets in 28 countries. Imaginarium SA was incorporated in 1992 and is headquartered in [[Zaragoza, Spain]].
